### Subscription Tiers
```
Free:        $0       20 credits, 100MB vault, 3 files, 10 tx/mo
Starter:     $0.99/mo 100 credits, 1GB vault, 50 files, $0.30 SOL gas
Researcher:  $3.99/mo 500 credits, 5GB vault, 500 files, $0.60 SOL gas
Pro:         $9.99/mo 1,500 credits, 25GB vault, unlimited files, $1.50 SOL gas
Institution: $29.99/mo 5,000 credits, 100GB vault, 10 seats, $5.00 SOL gas
Enterprise:  $99.99/mo 20,000 credits, 1TB vault, 50 seats, $15.00 SOL gas
Annual:      20% discount on all paid tiers
